                           <desc>Mediocre; it is characterized by thick vertical lines, hair lines (cp. ፈ፣ ነ፣ ከ፣ኀ፣ ራ), bifurcated elements (cp. ተ፣ ቊ፣ ድ፣ ዮ፣ ጽ). 
